text: Lauren Alaina Kristine Suddeth (born November 8, 1994) is an American country singer. She placed second on the 10th season of American Idol. Her album Wildflower was released in 2011. She is from Rossville, Georgia. ==Discography== ;Singles *"Doin' Fine" (2017) ==References== Category:Country musicians from Georgia (U.S state) Category:1994 births Category:Living people Category:Singers from Georgia (U.S. state) Category:American Idol contestants
